SCOPE
=====

This LICENSE file applies ONLY to the software components of this repository.

In scope (MIT License, below):
- Astro framework configuration and build scripts (astro.config.mjs,
  package.json, tsconfig.json)
- Custom Astro components and layouts (src/components/, src/layouts/)
- TypeScript/JavaScript utility code
- Page templates (the .astro structural code in src/pages/)

Out of scope (all rights reserved — see NOTICE.md):
- Page content and textual material (the prose, headings, and copy authored
  within src/pages/ and src/pages/newsletter/)
- The MEMoPAD name, wordmark, and any associated visual brand identity
- All images, graphics, illustrations, screenshots, and visual assets in
  public/ (including but not limited to hero images, prototype UI mockups,
  partner logos used by permission, photographs, and favicons)
- All PDF documents in public/ (including one-pager briefs)
- Newsletter content and any blog/article material

For permissions on out-of-scope materials, contact:
hello@luigimoretti.com

See NOTICE.md for the complete scope breakdown.

